Package cern.accsoft.steering.jmad.modeldefs.domain

Interface JMadModelDefinition

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ModelFileDependant
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractModelDefinition, JMadModelDefinitionImpl
    public interface JMadModelDefinition
extends ModelFileDependant
    This interface represents a general definition of a model-configuration for jmad. It can be implemented directly by a class, which provides a configuration.

      • getModelPackUri

        java.lang.String getModelPackUri()
        Returns:
        the URI to the origin model pack of the model definition. This URI can be used with jmad-modelpack-service to retrieve this definition at a later time. If this definition was not loaded from a model pack, null is returned. Unlike getSourceInformation(), this provides a more "high level" view on the origin location, independent of the (possibly temporary) location in the file system.
